{"tid":882631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不賣了？ 美大豆船原擬赴支開到一半改去...","createTime":"2018-10-30T09:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-30T10:09:58.000Z","uid":32511,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd1dc3706527cec453d2075689f48125aafa86f7","tid":882631,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:14:05.000Z","msg":"美中貿易戰持續中，大豆被視為戰場上的核心商品，遭中國課稅反擊，中國近幾個月來主要轉向巴西購買大豆，但美國大豆仍有出口對象，一艘運有近7萬公噸大豆的商船，原擬航向青島，卻在途中更改目的地朝越南航行。<br />\n <br />\n據《彭博》報導，一艘大型散貨船「Audacity」載有69244公噸大豆，10月21日從西雅圖出發，原本目的為青島，不過出海6天後變更航向，駛向越南；報導指出，受到美中貿易戰影響，美國出口中國的大豆大幅下滑，不過今年美國出口越南的大豆進口暴增93%。<br />\n <br />\n我國也和美國簽署價值15.6億美元（約474.96億元台幣）的大豆採購意向書，決定未來兩年向美國購買多達390萬噸大豆。"},{"pid":"cf16ce44324601609e90e310f38bb183d5acabe3","tid":882631,"uid":11598,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f6/Audacity_Logo.svg/2000px-Audacity_Logo.svg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2Ff%2Ff6%2FAudacity_Logo.svg%2F2000px-Audacity_Logo.svg.png&h=36fa8496&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59933b7fa4ed11e5e2906ca3a9b3bf980d36a548","tid":882631,"uid":8410,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:17:27.000Z","msg":"強國最後又係高價同越南買返， 越南fat fat <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"622e49d78309ad40cc91ccc87646a1f69d89994a","tid":882631,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"其實支那人玩野je<br />\n落香港洗白返上去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812d36a83cdf681d726638c220819d1e637df1e5","tid":882631,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T09:57:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ac7b728e7f363b85153ca0781f532b48dc00653","tid":882631,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59933b7fa4ed11e5e2906c